column5: I have a favourite musky bait that is no longer made. I would like to have another 10 of them made. Anyone know of any builders? Willing to be 40 each for good work.
You may want to pm outlaw George is a good bait builder
Give Kyle a shout. He makes some awesome lures! I have no affiliation with him or the company, just know a good product when I see it. http://www.johnstonlurecompany.com
Not sure you will get what you want for $40 per....going rate for custom wood is probably twice that or more.
